Ye actually past lead actually agar leads aaya hota aur aapke paas matlab sold out mein hota to at least past leads mein dikhta but past leads mein bhi nahi dikh raha hai kuch.

Customer: Haan haan.
Executive: Thik hai main aapko update karti hu jo revert.
Customer: Irrelevant lead nahi hai jo idhar udhar ki jyada aa rahi hai.
Executive: Acha acha. Thik hai hmm.
Executive: Main aapko batati hu thik hai mail aapko.
